import { Button, Box, TextField, Typography } from "@mui/material";

export default function AddNewClient({ onChange, addVehicle }) {
  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        mx: 4,
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "column",
        alignItems: "center",
      }}
    >
      <Typography component="h1" variant="h5">
        Add Vehicle
      </Typography>
      <Box noValidate sx={{ mt: 1 }}>
        <TextField
          margin="normal"
          required
          fullWidth
          id="ownerIdentityNumber"
          label="owner Identity Number"
          name="ownerIdentityNumber"
          autoFocus
          onChange={onChange}
        />
        <Box sx={{ display: "flex", gap: "0.5rem" }}>
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            id="chassisNumber"
            label="chassis Number"
            name="chassisNumber"
            fullWidth
            onChange={onChange}
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            id="registrationNumber"
            label="registration Number"
            name="registrationNumber"
            fullWidth
            onChange={onChange}
          />
        </Box>
        <Box sx={{ display: "flex", gap: "0.5rem" }}>
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            id="brand"
            label="brand"
            name="brand"
            type="string"
            fullWidth
            onChange={onChange}
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            id="model"
            label="model"
            name="model"
            type="string"
            fullWidth
            onChange={onChange}
          />
        </Box>
        <Box sx={{ display: "flex", gap: "0.5rem" }}>
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="yearOfManufacture"
            label="yearOfManufacture"
            name="yearOfManufacture"
            onChange={onChange}
            type="date"
              InputLabelProps={{
                shrink: true,
              }}
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="color"
            label="color"
            name="color"
            onChange={onChange}
          />
        </Box>
        <Box sx={{ display: "flex", gap: "0.5rem" }}>
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="mileage"
            label="mileage"
            name="mileage"
            onChange={onChange}
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="fuelType"
            label="fuelType"
            name="fuelType"
            type="string"
            onChange={onChange}
          />
        </Box>
        <Box sx={{ display: "flex", gap: "0.5rem" }}>
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="dateOfPurchase"
            label="dateOfPurchase"
            name="dateOfPurchase"
            onChange={onChange}
            type="date"
              
              InputLabelProps={{
                shrink: true,
              }}
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="vehicleCondition"
            label="vehicleCondition"
            name="vehicleCondition"
            type="vehicleCondition"
            onChange={onChange}
          />
        </Box>
        <Button
          type="submit"
          onClick={addVehicle}
          variant="contained"
          sx={{ mt: 3, mb: 1 }}
        >
          Add Vehicle
        </Button>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}
